{
  "stem": "6076.6",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The last minute, she feared.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I says, he took her out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They took out about, about 10 of them-- send them to that forest and to be killed.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We had a, a big box all winter standing near our barrack.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The people were laying there like sardines who died in that ward.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They took them to that box.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "When spring arrived, there came with a truck.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And they put that-- it was like a stick with a hook.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I watched them to put it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Once I worked in the day-- at night, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So I was in the daytime home.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I could-- I watched it, the way they came and took out these dead girls, the women out from that box which was next to my bunk and schlepping them on the truck.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And the neck, and an arm, and the stomach-- they put that hook like you, you drag a cat from the street, you know, in a box.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "That's the way he pulled these people on the truck.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Sometimes I stood there emotional.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "My mind didn't work.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And I says, oh, God, oh God.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "You know, some of the girls, I knew.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "But the same [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Batenschlager ?] did such evil things in camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "One January-- January 1941-- [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Batenschlager ?] with another one, his partner-- he had, we had [?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Killerman. ?] We had [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Batenschlager. ?] And he came to our camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And he walked into our barrack.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And he took out three most beautiful girls on New Years' Eve.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "One was Chanka Melechman.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "She was a friend of mine.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "One was from [INAUDIBLE]-- a girl which I forgot her name.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And the, the third one, I don't-- I did, I didn't know her.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "He took them out.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
